title: Stop Trying to Change the World
itunes:title: Stop Trying to Change the World
description:
Episode 146 -  The world doesn't need you to change it. What it needs you to do is to look inward and work on yourself. A lot of people ruin their lives by worrying about other people's experiences so in this episode I talk about controlling other people's experiences vs controlling your own.
